  "displayTitle": "AI Ethics and Responsible AI",
  "body": "<p>AI systems are transforming how we work, communicate and make decisions. As these technologies become more powerful and pervasive, the question of how to develop and deploy them ethically and responsibly has never been more important.</p><p>In this course, you'll explore the foundations of AI ethics, follow the AI lifecycle to see where ethical considerations apply in practice, and examine real-world case studies where things went wrong — and why.</p><p>This content was developed by TPXImpact.</p><p><strong>Select 'Introduction' to begin.</strong></p>",
